==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Excerption
<hw>Ex*cerp"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>excerptio</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of excerpting or
selecting.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>That which is selected or gleaned; an extract.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>His <qex>excerptions</qex> out of the Fathers.</q>
<rj><qau>Fuller.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Excerptive</ent>⟦br⟧
